{"tid":1431104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有心理準備加入反黑組嘅入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-08T02:06:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T03:38:56.000Z","uid":36008,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4cf66a784ee47f865afb44bd9cf3c34c88efbe2f","tid":1431104,"uid":36008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:06:12.000Z","msg":"依加啲黑社會用刀<br />\n<del>仲要可能喜馬拉雅山嗰200個刀手終於行到嚟香港</del><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位反黑組，或者隨時要反黑嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得防切割手套，護脛保護上五寸下五寸，同埋護陰！<br />\n<br />\n第五級防切割手套：<br />\nKOREL KG-CUT 防割手套 5D級 (最高等級)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bpYaGBR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbpYaGBR.jpg&h=2970695e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跆拳道散打護陰 (防止俾人錫春袋)<br />\n初時未習慣會感覺妨礙移動，建議加Vaseline使用<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MAixUXG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMAixUXG.png&h=fa8ef3fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我好擔心各位嘅安危<br />\n<br />\n以上講緊已經係反黑，或有意加入警察反黑組嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e1dc75510c278e1d9d3b46ca3f7a5ac0d1432ba","tid":1431104,"uid":36008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:07:00.000Z","msg":"開錯台，想開上班台"},{"pid":"5906f8bd58c2e62e8c8c12181dd37a44cd59d2c3","tid":1431104,"uid":36008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:07:10.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"048292bc44030c4b126ca580378768395cd97d15","tid":1431104,"uid":36008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:07:20.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"f37121eb2cb7f25b3cccf220d9fc9215ef82eb01","tid":1431104,"uid":36008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:07:32.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"dcc8c4cc5ea812c80ff3e759df4c58ca4a6bd912","tid":1431104,"uid":36008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl